      <link>https://github.com/arman-bd/guppylm</link>
      <description>Built a ~9M param LLM from scratch to understand how they actually work. Vanilla transformer, 60K synthetic conversations, ~130 lines of PyTorch. Trains in 5 min on a free Colab T4. The fish thinks the meaning of life is food.&lt;p&gt;Fork it and swap the personality for your own character.</description>
